text: Holger Lundgren (31 March 1912 - 12 May 1966) was a Swedish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Swedish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Sweden Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Örnsköldsvik Municipality
